1
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,320
Master Xuan is waiting in the tea room.

2
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:57,600
Coming.

3
00:01:57,880 --> 00:01:58,520
Coming.

4
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:03,240
Master Xuan, please, have a seat.

5
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:04,720
Okay, thank you.

6
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:14,720
You're getting fancier by the day.

7
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,920
Just showing up empty-handed,

8
00:02:16,920 --> 00:02:18,240
nothing but yourself.

9
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:23,400
Actually, just outside your gate,

10
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:25,200
I saw someone selling candied hawthorns.

11
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:26,440
I'll go grab you a stick.

12
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:27,720
I'm sour enough already.

13
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:38,280
So, what brings you here?

14
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,640
If you've got nothing to say,

15
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:43,000
then I'm off.

16
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:46,000
This is your house.

17
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:49,400
I'm off to walk the dog.

18
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:53,440
Dad.

19
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:54,360
Dad!

20
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:58,080
Master Xuan, don't take it to heart.

21
00:02:58,080 --> 00:02:59,400
I'll go along for the walk too.

22
00:03:09,880 --> 00:03:12,640
Master Jiang, driving while walking the dog?

23
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,640
Oh my goodness.

24
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:26,840
Lucky.

25
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,240
How's it going?

26
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,800
You tell me how it's going.

27
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,560
Are you walking the dog,

28
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:36,920
or walking me?

29
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,960
I'm just helping you cool off.

30
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:46,480
Come on.

31
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:47,960
Good stuff.

32
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:49,320
Once you leave Beijing,

33
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,720
you can't get this anywhere.

34
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:14,400
What is this? What even is this?

35
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:17,360
Guess you can't handle the good stuff, huh?

36
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:23,920
Is what's in our two bowls

37
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:25,520
really the same thing?

38
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:36,160
Authentic.

39
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:38,800
What's in the bowls is the same.

40
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:40,320
But what's in our heads

41
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,280
isn't the same.

42
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:45,760
What's not the same?

43
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,240
You know it yourself.

44
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,920
I get it now.

45
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:04,960
Manager Xu must've called you.

46
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:06,200
Because

47
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:09,000
I'm the one who asked him for your address.

48
00:05:09,520 --> 00:05:11,840
Even if Manager Xu told me you were coming,

49
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:14,000
was I supposed to greet you ten miles out?

50
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:17,040
You knew I was coming.

51
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,800
Why bother with all this useless stuff?

52
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:22,000
Just get to the point.

53
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,080
I've got nothing to say.

54
00:05:23,080 --> 00:05:23,440
Right.

55
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,480
You don't have anything to say.

56
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,480
But I do.

57
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:28,200
I came to you with something.

58
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:30,000
I'm here asking a favor.

59
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:32,280
Go on then.

60
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:34,080
Are you willing to help or not?

61
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:37,240
Is that any way to ask for a favor?

62
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,520
Name your terms.

63
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,200
Just say it.

64
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:44,560
Name my terms?

65
00:05:46,400 --> 00:05:47,800
What do I even lack?

66
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:49,160
That's some big talk.

67
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:51,120
What could you give me?

68
00:05:55,880 --> 00:05:56,680
Just this.

69
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:57,760
How much?

70
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,560
I'll pay.

71
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:06,520
I see you're at least somewhat sincere.

72
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:08,960
I don't want anything from you.

73
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:12,240
I just want an honest judgment.

74
00:06:17,840 --> 00:06:18,760
This sheet of paper here,

75
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,480
it's the extra-clean six-foot single sheet

76
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:23,240
you made during the 1997 Spring Equinox.

77
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,200
Take a look yourself.

78
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:25,200
What's wrong with it?

79
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:33,640
What's wrong with it?

80
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,040
See for yourself.

81
00:07:20,760 --> 00:07:21,720
There's nothing wrong with it.

82
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:23,640
Fine and flawless.

83
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:25,360
Cloud patterns like snow.

84
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:27,040
Tough as ox tendon.

85
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:29,000
You've really got some nerve

86
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,560
singing your own praises like that.

87
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:31,920
If you ask me to look at this paper,

88
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:35,040
Dull and lackluster.

89
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:37,520
Uneven texture.

90
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:39,600
Am I right or not?

91
00:07:41,280 --> 00:07:43,320
If you can't take a bit of criticism,

92
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:45,040
then just stay holed up in the mountains.

93
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,240
Don't bother coming out.

94
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:50,920
If you ask me, this stack of paper,

95
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:51,840
just watch.

96
00:08:05,960 --> 00:08:07,160
The ink spreads unevenly.

97
00:08:07,880 --> 00:08:08,800
Now look at the writing.

98
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:14,960
Rough and sluggish.

99
00:08:15,520 --> 00:08:17,520
Like an old ox plowing a field.

100
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:18,760
Tell me,

101
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:20,280
am I right?

102
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:26,520
Stop huffing.

103
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:28,840
You came all this way.

104
00:08:28,840 --> 00:08:30,200
I don't want to make things hard for you.

105
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:31,600
I'll just ask you one question.

106
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:33,360
If your answer satisfies me,

107
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:36,200
I'll personally call the chairman of Songhezhai.

108
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:38,159
I'll handle your matter.

109
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:39,960
Answer me this.

110
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:41,799
Between the two of us,

111
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,080
you and me,

112
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:46,000
who knows jack shit

113
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,640
about paper,

114
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:52,600
and understands absolutely nothing?

115
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:56,600
I'll give you one answer.

116
00:08:57,880 --> 00:08:58,720
When it comes to paper,

117
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:03,080
you, Jiang Ziliu,

118
00:09:03,880 --> 00:09:06,560
know jack shit and understand nothing.

119
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:17,520
Stubborn mule.

120
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:46,920
Manager Xu.

121
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:54,440
Manager Xu wants to visit our factory.

122
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,000
No, no, no.

123
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:56,440
No, no.

124
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:58,400
Of course Manager Xu is welcome to visit.

125
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,240
Welcome, welcome.

126
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:02,880
Who was that?

127
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:08,240
Jiang Ziliu called your boss.

128
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:11,920
Manager Xu.

129
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:13,640
You...

130
00:10:14,240 --> 00:10:15,440
You're not mistaken, are you?

131
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:18,360
No.

132
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:19,440
Welcome.

133
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,760
Manager Xu is welcome to come.

134
00:10:20,800 --> 00:10:21,960
Welcome, Manager Xu.

135
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:32,920
That old fellow.

136
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:38,040
Good news!

137
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:39,400
I could see you smiling from far away.

138
00:10:39,400 --> 00:10:40,400
You bet.

139
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:41,120
Yes, yes.

140
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:41,880
Just think about it.

141
00:10:41,880 --> 00:10:44,400
Old Xuan's trip to Beijing wasn't wasted.

142
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:45,120
Of course.

143
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:46,880
And everyone's hard work paid off too.

144
00:10:46,880 --> 00:10:48,240
I've already decided.

145
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:50,880
If this deal goes through,

146
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:52,720
I'll give everyone a raise first.

147
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,160
Thank you, Madam. Thank you.

148
00:10:54,160 --> 00:10:55,280
No matter how much,

149
00:10:55,280 --> 00:10:57,240
it's just a token of my appreciation.

150
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,240
You don't have to say that.

151
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,640
We trust you.

152
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:02,280
Your master also said,

153
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:03,760
he said,

154
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:06,720
we should make more paper.

155
00:11:06,880 --> 00:11:08,760
They want to check our inventory.

156
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:10,000
When they place their order,

157
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:10,840
we can't be out of stock.

158
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:11,400
Right?

159
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:12,080
Right.

160
00:11:12,160 --> 00:11:14,000
We must guarantee the quality of the paper.

161
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:14,520
Okay?

162
00:11:14,520 --> 00:11:15,240
Okay, okay.

163
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,000
Don't you worry.

164
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:18,000
Every single vat today,

165
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,960
I'll have them running at full speed.

166
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:20,600
Good.

167
00:11:20,720 --> 00:11:22,360
Brothers, let's get to work!

168
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:22,880
Get to work!

169
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:23,760
Okay, okay, okay.

170
00:11:24,280 --> 00:11:25,400
I'm counting on you.

171
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:26,480
I'm heading to the other workshops,

172
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:27,720
I'll go tell them too.

173
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:28,160
Madam, take it easy.

174
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:28,960
Counting on you.

175
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:30,240
Careful, careful, Madam.

176
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:38,360
Master Ye, got a minute?

177
00:11:38,760 --> 00:11:39,600
Sure, talk.

178
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:40,400
Won't take long.

179
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:43,120
Same thing as before.

180
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:46,040
I'd like you to help make some ancient-method paper.

181
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:49,480
You've been slacking on paper-making lately.

182
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:51,400
Either you're nowhere to be found,

183
00:11:51,400 --> 00:11:52,240
or else,

184
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:53,880
you're off tinkering by yourself.

185
00:11:53,880 --> 00:11:54,880
So this is what it's about.

186
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:56,240
I want to give it a shot.

187
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:57,480
I think it's a real opportunity.

188
00:11:57,640 --> 00:11:58,600
Go ahead, try.

189
00:11:58,760 --> 00:12:00,120
I really don't have the time.

190
00:12:00,120 --> 00:12:02,160
Can't you see how busy we are?

191
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:04,640
Songhezhai is coming any moment.

192
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:05,400
Besides,

193
00:12:05,640 --> 00:12:06,640
what about old Xuan?

194
00:12:06,640 --> 00:12:08,000
He never mentioned any of this.

195
00:12:08,040 --> 00:12:08,840
Am I right?

196
00:12:09,120 --> 00:12:11,000
It won't take much of your time.

197
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:11,360
Just...

198
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:12,120
No way.

199
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:13,400
I'm busy.

200
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:15,120
Magan!

201
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:15,840
Come.

202
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:16,480
Alright.

203
00:12:18,640 --> 00:12:19,720
Quick, hold it steady.

204
00:12:21,400 --> 00:12:24,160
Upon seeing the princess steal the command arrow,

205
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:26,000
my heart cannot help but rejoice.

206
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:31,000
Standing at the palace gate, I call out...

207
00:12:31,920 --> 00:12:32,720
Forget it.

208
00:12:34,920 --> 00:12:35,640
Too high.

209
00:12:35,640 --> 00:12:36,400
Xiao Yu.

210
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:40,120
What's up?

211
00:12:40,640 --> 00:12:43,360
Can you help make paper for a couple of days?

212
00:12:44,040 --> 00:12:44,840
Lift the screen.

213
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:45,760
You've done it before.

214
00:12:45,760 --> 00:12:46,520
It's simple.

215
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:47,760
Just scooping paper.

216
00:12:49,040 --> 00:12:49,880
Zhang Du.

217
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:51,520
Uncle Laokezi.

218
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:53,520
What are you two up to?

219
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:54,520
I, I...

220
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:56,120
Nothing much.

221
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:57,520
We're just talking about private stuff.

222
00:12:57,520 --> 00:12:58,600
I wasn't talking about anything.

223
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:00,160
It's working hours.

224
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:01,840
What private stuff are you chatting about?

225
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:02,640
Get back to work.

226
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:04,360
I'm going right now.

227
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:15,640
Just help me make paper for two days.

228
00:13:16,040 --> 00:13:17,040
Think you can do it?

229
00:13:18,040 --> 00:13:19,000
Making it, sure.

230
00:13:19,640 --> 00:13:20,600
But it depends on how.

231
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:21,280
Right?

232
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:24,640
I'll pay you, I'll pay.

233
00:13:28,040 --> 00:13:29,040
Is this enough?

234
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:37,520
I...

235
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:39,360
See, I knew you were a reasonable guy.

236
00:13:39,520 --> 00:13:40,360
When do we start?

237
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:41,760
How about now?

238
00:13:41,760 --> 00:13:42,880
Let's go, let's go.

239
00:13:44,760 --> 00:13:45,560
A bit deeper.

240
00:13:46,680 --> 00:13:47,480
Zhang Du!

241
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:49,800
Who told you to make ancient-method paper?

242
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:51,880
Nobody.

243
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:53,920
I decided to make ancient-method paper myself.

244
00:13:56,520 --> 00:13:59,000
Don't you know what your master's wife said?

245
00:13:59,280 --> 00:14:00,560
Stop right now, stop it.

246
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:05,880
Xiao Yu.

247
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:07,600
At a time like this,

248
00:14:07,640 --> 00:14:09,080
you're joining in this nonsense too?

249
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:18,040
Master said the factory would be Zhang Du's to run.

250
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:20,120
So I've got to listen to him.

251
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:21,120
Nonsense.

252
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:23,760
Old Xuan gave orders before he left,

253
00:14:24,240 --> 00:14:25,480
that senior brother would be in charge.

254
00:14:26,520 --> 00:14:27,960
Well, nobody told me that.

255
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:29,040
I never heard it.

256
00:14:29,040 --> 00:14:30,400
Then I'm telling you right now.

257
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:31,640
But what you say doesn't count.

258
00:14:31,840 --> 00:14:32,400
Why, you...

259
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:33,160
Come on, Xiao Yu.

260
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:35,040
What?

261
00:14:36,640 --> 00:14:37,400
Fine.

262
00:14:39,160 --> 00:14:40,640
When your master gets back,

263
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:42,960
let's see how you two explain this.

264
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:45,520
Magan, let's go.

265
00:14:48,640 --> 00:14:49,040
Get to it.

266
00:15:04,200 --> 00:15:05,080
Come on, keep going.

267
00:15:07,760 --> 00:15:09,960
I told old Xuan on the phone.

268
00:15:10,640 --> 00:15:12,400
He just gave me three words.

269
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:14,840
"Let him be."

270
00:15:21,680 --> 00:15:25,560
He wasn't named successor this time.

271
00:15:25,640 --> 00:15:28,200
He's bound to feel a bit upset.

272
00:15:28,200 --> 00:15:29,160
Besides,

273
00:15:29,560 --> 00:15:30,960
old Xuan also said,

274
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:32,600
we owe this kid.

275
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:34,240
So just let him be.

276
00:15:37,040 --> 00:15:38,440
Whether he scoops more or less,

277
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:40,800
it doesn't really matter.

278
00:15:41,720 --> 00:15:43,160
I just don't know what this kid

279
00:15:43,640 --> 00:15:44,840
is really up to.

280
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:46,880
Hope he doesn't stir up trouble.

281
00:15:48,080 --> 00:15:48,880
Senior brother,

282
00:15:49,480 --> 00:15:50,880
Zhang Du, that kid,

283
00:15:51,120 --> 00:15:51,920
he...

284
00:15:52,160 --> 00:15:54,800
He's stubborn, but not malicious.

285
00:15:55,120 --> 00:15:57,720
What kind of trouble could he cause?

286
00:15:58,320 --> 00:15:59,640
Don't overthink it.

287
00:16:06,240 --> 00:16:07,840
They've come to inspect already.

288
00:16:08,040 --> 00:16:09,800
They probably won't back out now.

289
00:16:10,240 --> 00:16:11,320
Don't worry, auntie.

290
00:16:11,360 --> 00:16:12,880
Since they came all this way,

291
00:16:12,880 --> 00:16:14,200
it's basically a done deal.

292
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:15,480
That's good then.

293
00:16:16,360 --> 00:16:18,360
But Master Xuan Yan came too.

294
00:16:18,360 --> 00:16:19,400
Xuan Yan isn't coming today.

295
00:16:19,400 --> 00:16:20,400
I called him,

296
00:16:20,400 --> 00:16:21,720
but his phone's always off.

297
00:16:21,760 --> 00:16:23,120
No idea what he's busy with.

298
00:16:23,280 --> 00:16:24,480
I can't reach him either.

299
00:16:24,480 --> 00:16:25,760
He sent me a message last week,

300
00:16:25,760 --> 00:16:26,800
saying he's in seclusion.

301
00:16:27,960 --> 00:16:29,360
He'd better not have become a monk!

302
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:31,280
No way, auntie.

303
00:16:37,560 --> 00:16:37,920
The car's here.

304
00:16:37,920 --> 00:16:38,680
They're here, they're here!

305
00:16:42,400 --> 00:16:43,040
Careful now.

306
00:16:49,280 --> 00:16:50,240
Master, Master.

307
00:16:50,240 --> 00:16:51,480
You're back, you're back.

308
00:16:51,480 --> 00:16:52,400
Thanks for coming all this way.

309
00:16:54,360 --> 00:16:55,000
Come, come.

310
00:16:55,880 --> 00:16:57,680
Let me introduce everyone.

311
00:16:57,880 --> 00:17:00,800
This is Manager Xu from Songhezhai in Beijing.

312
00:17:00,800 --> 00:17:02,280
Welcome, welcome!

313
00:17:02,280 --> 00:17:03,600
Hello, everyone.

314
00:17:04,280 --> 00:17:05,079
Manager Xu.

315
00:17:05,079 --> 00:17:06,960
Come, let's take a tour of the factory.

316
00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:07,240
Sure.

317
00:17:07,240 --> 00:17:07,720
Take a look around.

318
00:17:07,720 --> 00:17:08,160
This way, please.

319
00:17:08,160 --> 00:17:09,319
Alright, alright.

320
00:17:12,880 --> 00:17:13,880
Aren't you going to introduce me?

321
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:15,880
Master Jiang.

322
00:17:16,520 --> 00:17:18,960
You're the famous Master Jiang.

323
00:17:18,960 --> 00:17:20,400
Who wouldn't know you?

324
00:17:22,599 --> 00:17:24,040
Master Jiang, welcome.

325
00:17:25,359 --> 00:17:26,000
You...

326
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:29,320
You dare show your face to me?

327
00:17:30,680 --> 00:17:32,440
Our boss went to a meeting at the county.

328
00:17:32,440 --> 00:17:33,640
He asked us to receive you.

329
00:17:35,160 --> 00:17:35,880
I wouldn't dare.

330
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:39,120
Sister-in-law, what's for lunch?

331
00:17:39,360 --> 00:17:39,880
Steamed eggs with qin fish.

332
00:17:39,880 --> 00:17:40,360
Let's go.

333
00:17:40,360 --> 00:17:41,600
Everything's ready.

334
00:17:41,760 --> 00:17:42,760
And also that...

335
00:17:42,760 --> 00:17:44,400
We've got Maolin stew too.

336
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:47,200
That's exactly what I came for.

337
00:17:48,840 --> 00:17:51,240
Master Jiang, our Old Xuan said

338
00:17:51,640 --> 00:17:52,480
to thank you.

339
00:17:52,480 --> 00:17:53,880
For helping us out so much.

340
00:17:54,120 --> 00:17:55,120
Him? Thank me?

341
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:57,280
Yeah, right, who'd believe that.

342
00:17:58,000 --> 00:17:58,840
It's true.

343
00:18:03,520 --> 00:18:04,840
Everyone, listen up.

344
00:18:05,120 --> 00:18:08,480
In a bit, Master Jiang and Manager Xu

345
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:10,240
will be coming here for a tour.

346
00:18:10,520 --> 00:18:11,320
So,

347
00:18:11,360 --> 00:18:14,760
everyone show your very best work.

348
00:18:14,880 --> 00:18:16,560
Don't let me down, whatever you do.

349
00:18:16,560 --> 00:18:17,360
Got it?

350
00:18:17,360 --> 00:18:18,000
Yes!

351
00:18:21,040 --> 00:18:22,000
Where's Zhang Du?

352
00:18:22,600 --> 00:18:23,360
Him?

353
00:18:23,360 --> 00:18:24,520
He went to find Master Jiang.

354
00:18:24,520 --> 00:18:25,360
As for other mills,

355
00:18:25,360 --> 00:18:26,520
I can't really say.

356
00:18:26,520 --> 00:18:28,840
But the Xuan family makes Xuan paper

357
00:18:29,120 --> 00:18:30,520
with only three ingredients.

358
00:18:30,720 --> 00:18:32,000
First, blue sandalwood bark.

359
00:18:32,240 --> 00:18:34,440
Second, sandy-field rice straw.

360
00:18:34,520 --> 00:18:35,480
And third,

361
00:18:35,480 --> 00:18:37,320
top-quality mountain spring water.

362
00:18:37,640 --> 00:18:41,000
I channeled the spring water from deep in the mountains.

363
00:18:41,240 --> 00:18:42,760
Piped it in from the mountains.

364
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:44,640
That's no short distance.

365
00:18:45,840 --> 00:18:46,640
Five kilometers.

366
00:18:47,120 --> 00:18:48,600
A huge undertaking, huge.

367
00:18:48,680 --> 00:18:49,600
Excellent, excellent.

368
00:18:49,600 --> 00:18:51,080
Fine craftsmanship deserves fine materials.

369
00:18:51,080 --> 00:18:52,360
I wasn't kidding, was I?

370
00:18:52,440 --> 00:18:53,600
That's what dedication looks like.

371
00:18:55,080 --> 00:18:56,960
Elder Jiang, you've come such a long way.

372
00:18:56,960 --> 00:18:58,080
Why not rest a bit first?

373
00:18:58,160 --> 00:19:00,120
I'll head up to see the water source.

374
00:19:00,120 --> 00:19:01,120
Just this detail alone

375
00:19:01,120 --> 00:19:03,480
fully shows the Xuan family's dedication.

376
00:19:03,480 --> 00:19:04,200
Thank you.

377
00:19:04,520 --> 00:19:04,960
I...

378
00:19:04,960 --> 00:19:06,800
I need to go up and take some photos.

379
00:19:06,800 --> 00:19:08,480
To go back and give our boss

380
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:09,520
a proper report.

381
00:19:09,800 --> 00:19:11,040
You need to take a good look.

382
00:19:11,400 --> 00:19:12,280
Then I'll wait right here

383
00:19:12,840 --> 00:19:14,360
for your good news.

384
00:19:29,240 --> 00:19:31,440
I can manage stir-fries and soups just fine.

385
00:19:31,480 --> 00:19:32,840
But this Maolin stew,

386
00:19:32,920 --> 00:19:35,040
only our Sister Xiumei can pull it off.

387
00:19:35,240 --> 00:19:36,040
That's right.

388
00:19:36,080 --> 00:19:38,800
The thing is, Jiang Ziliu is too picky.

389
00:19:38,800 --> 00:19:39,760
You can't fool him.

390
00:19:40,760 --> 00:19:41,520
Madam,

391
00:19:42,560 --> 00:19:43,440
here's the light soy sauce.

392
00:19:43,520 --> 00:19:44,840
That's just what I was waiting for.

393
00:19:46,360 --> 00:19:47,040
Smells amazing.

394
00:19:47,600 --> 00:19:48,200
Right?

395
00:19:48,200 --> 00:19:50,560
Xiaoman, grab some scallions from the backyard.

396
00:19:50,560 --> 00:19:51,240
Okay.

397
00:19:57,960 --> 00:19:59,160
Manager Xu, take a look.

398
00:19:59,160 --> 00:20:00,400
These pipes here,

399
00:20:01,040 --> 00:20:01,480
And then?

400
00:20:01,480 --> 00:20:02,280
What we do is,

401
00:20:02,560 --> 00:20:05,280
we lay these pipes to channel the spring,

402
00:20:05,400 --> 00:20:08,120
down to the reservoir at the hill's foot.

403
00:20:08,320 --> 00:20:09,120
And this area here,

404
00:20:09,280 --> 00:20:10,440
this is the sandy-field rice.

405
00:20:10,720 --> 00:20:12,400
Everyone, take a look at this rice.

406
00:20:12,400 --> 00:20:13,920
This is what we use to make Xuan paper.

407
00:20:14,160 --> 00:20:16,240
And this rice is very special.

408
00:20:31,080 --> 00:20:33,760
Boss Xuan, your staff meals are quite the feast.

409
00:20:34,160 --> 00:20:35,760
Do the workers usually eat like this?

410
00:20:35,920 --> 00:20:38,240
Today's table has two more dishes.

411
00:20:38,520 --> 00:20:39,440
Qin fish steamed with eggs,

412
00:20:39,440 --> 00:20:40,480
and the Maolin stew.

413
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:41,680
Both are my favorites.

414
00:20:42,480 --> 00:20:43,600
I get it, I get it.

415
00:20:44,280 --> 00:20:46,400
You treat your workers so well, no doubt.

416
00:20:46,920 --> 00:20:47,960
This is nothing.

417
00:20:48,160 --> 00:20:50,240
Manager Xu, I'll be honest with you.

418
00:20:50,720 --> 00:20:54,320
Among all private paper mills in Taohua Town,

419
00:20:54,560 --> 00:20:58,160
we Xuans have always paid social insurance.

420
00:20:58,200 --> 00:20:59,520
Insurance and all that,

421
00:20:59,600 --> 00:21:01,520
never interrupted for all these years.

422
00:21:02,400 --> 00:21:03,200
And on top of that,

423
00:21:04,880 --> 00:21:06,000
our wages

424
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:08,000
are a bit higher than at other mills.

425
00:21:08,800 --> 00:21:12,720
I heard Songhezhai was the same in the old days.

426
00:21:12,720 --> 00:21:14,760
Just like family.

427
00:21:14,760 --> 00:21:16,000
Really warm and personal.

428
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:16,440
Right?

429
00:21:17,120 --> 00:21:18,360
Heart for heart, that's how it works.

430
00:21:18,520 --> 00:21:19,560
Yes, yes, exactly.

431
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:21,400
To make a good sheet of paper,

432
00:21:21,840 --> 00:21:23,600
you first need a sincere heart.

433
00:21:23,600 --> 00:21:24,400
Yes, yes.

434
00:21:24,800 --> 00:21:28,280
When the boss and workers get along like this,

435
00:21:28,280 --> 00:21:29,760
how could they fail to make good paper?

436
00:21:29,760 --> 00:21:30,520
Am I right?

437
00:21:31,600 --> 00:21:32,400
Then come on,

438
00:21:33,760 --> 00:21:35,000
stop putting on airs.

439
00:21:35,000 --> 00:21:35,800
I'm not putting on airs.

440
00:21:35,800 --> 00:21:36,560
I'm raising my glass.

441
00:21:36,640 --> 00:21:37,440
No,

442
00:21:37,840 --> 00:21:39,160
I really must raise a glass.

443
00:21:39,360 --> 00:21:40,680
I insist on raising one.

444
00:21:41,400 --> 00:21:42,280
Boss Xuan,

445
00:21:42,840 --> 00:21:44,360
with your character,

446
00:21:44,440 --> 00:21:46,240
with your dedication,

447
00:21:47,080 --> 00:21:49,320
your paper simply can't go wrong.

448
00:21:49,680 --> 00:21:51,920
Let's have a good talk about our partnership.

449
00:21:51,920 --> 00:21:52,760
Here's to you.

450
00:21:52,800 --> 00:21:54,440
That's exactly what I've been waiting to hear.

451
00:21:54,440 --> 00:21:55,240
Manager Xu,

452
00:21:55,280 --> 00:21:56,240
come, here's to you.

453
00:21:56,240 --> 00:21:57,240
Here's to you, here's to you.

454
00:21:57,240 --> 00:21:58,240
To you, to you.

455
00:21:58,600 --> 00:21:59,440
After you.

456
00:22:00,400 --> 00:22:00,720
Come on.

457
00:22:00,720 --> 00:22:01,320
Come, come, come.

458
00:22:01,320 --> 00:22:01,560
I,

459
00:22:01,560 --> 00:22:02,000
here's to you, to you.

460
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:03,200
I'll join you, I'll join you.

461
00:22:03,200 --> 00:22:03,960
All right, all right.

462
00:22:04,440 --> 00:22:05,040
Good.

463
00:22:05,320 --> 00:22:06,240
Thanks for your hard work.

464
00:22:11,920 --> 00:22:12,240
Come, come, come.

465
00:22:12,240 --> 00:22:12,560
Watch your step.

466
00:22:12,560 --> 00:22:13,240
Please, have a seat.

467
00:22:13,240 --> 00:22:13,760
Help yourself.

468
00:22:13,760 --> 00:22:14,200
Alright, alright.

469
00:22:14,200 --> 00:22:15,000
Give it a try.

470
00:22:15,160 --> 00:22:16,400
These little fish

471
00:22:16,400 --> 00:22:17,800
were caught this morning

472
00:22:17,920 --> 00:22:19,320
fresh from the creek.

473
00:22:19,320 --> 00:22:20,400
Wonderful, wonderful.

474
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:21,200
Manager Xu,

475
00:22:21,880 --> 00:22:23,760
thanks for supporting Peach Blossom Town.

476
00:22:24,040 --> 00:22:25,160
I can't really drink,

477
00:22:25,160 --> 00:22:26,680
but I have to show my appreciation.

478
00:22:26,680 --> 00:22:27,560
Here's a toast to you.

479
00:22:27,560 --> 00:22:28,000
Thank you, thank you.

480
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:29,160
This girl is really something.

481
00:22:29,800 --> 00:22:31,240
If you don't sign the contract today,

482
00:22:31,240 --> 00:22:32,240
you won't even make it out that door.

483
00:22:32,240 --> 00:22:33,040
Alright, alright.

484
00:22:33,080 --> 00:22:34,760
I'll sign it right away.

485
00:22:34,760 --> 00:22:35,520
Take it easy.

486
00:22:36,920 --> 00:22:37,400
Okay.

487
00:22:42,440 --> 00:22:43,040
Alright.

488
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:44,800
Master Jiang, please don't say that.

489
00:22:44,800 --> 00:22:46,200
Let me make it up to you, okay?

490
00:22:46,920 --> 00:22:47,520
Alright.

491
00:22:47,520 --> 00:22:48,760
Let's have one together, then.

492
00:22:49,040 --> 00:22:49,880
Just a little bit.

493
00:22:50,520 --> 00:22:51,360
Take it easy, take it easy.

494
00:22:56,520 --> 00:22:57,560
Please, dig in.

495
00:22:57,560 --> 00:22:58,040
Okay.

496
00:22:58,680 --> 00:22:59,480
Manager Xu.

497
00:22:59,560 --> 00:23:00,360
Master Jiang.

498
00:23:00,440 --> 00:23:01,360
Master, Madam.

499
00:23:01,520 --> 00:23:02,280
I'm full.

500
00:23:02,280 --> 00:23:03,320
I've got things to do.

501
00:23:03,320 --> 00:23:04,560
Please, take your time.

502
00:23:05,080 --> 00:23:05,520
Alright.

503
00:23:05,520 --> 00:23:06,240
So then...

504
00:23:10,400 --> 00:23:11,000
Come on, come on.

505
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:11,600
Try some of this.

506
00:23:11,600 --> 00:23:12,560
Okay, okay.

507
00:23:14,240 --> 00:23:15,320
How does it taste?

508
00:23:38,560 --> 00:23:39,200
Squad Leader Ye

509
00:23:39,800 --> 00:23:40,600
Have you seen Zhang Du?

510
00:23:40,600 --> 00:23:41,520
No, I haven't.

511
00:23:46,640 --> 00:23:47,480
Please, try this. It's free-range chicken.

512
00:23:47,480 --> 00:23:48,000
Sure.

513
00:23:48,000 --> 00:23:50,760
Boss Xuan, I never dawdle in business.

514
00:23:50,760 --> 00:23:53,120
Once I'm back, I'll set you up

515
00:23:53,120 --> 00:23:55,280
with a long-term strategic contract.

516
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:58,600
From now on, Songhezhai's yearly orders

517
00:23:58,720 --> 00:23:59,840
will all come to you.

518
00:24:00,000 --> 00:24:01,400
And the quantity...

519
00:24:01,400 --> 00:24:01,880
Manager Xu.

520
00:24:01,880 --> 00:24:02,280
Zhang Du.

521
00:24:02,280 --> 00:24:03,040
Master Jiang.

522
00:24:03,040 --> 00:24:03,400
Zhang Du.

523
00:24:03,400 --> 00:24:04,400
I need to trouble you all.

524
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:05,560
Could you please help me?

525
00:24:05,560 --> 00:24:06,040
Help, help me out with...

526
00:24:06,040 --> 00:24:06,760
No rush, no rush.

527
00:24:06,760 --> 00:24:07,680
We'll talk later.

528
00:24:07,800 --> 00:24:08,520
There's no hurry.

529
00:24:08,520 --> 00:24:09,120
Manager Xu.

530
00:24:09,120 --> 00:24:09,720
Zhang Du.

531
00:24:11,040 --> 00:24:11,680
Just let him be.

532
00:24:14,200 --> 00:24:15,640
Manager Xu, Master Jiang.

533
00:24:15,840 --> 00:24:17,280
I'd like the two of you to take a look.

534
00:24:17,320 --> 00:24:19,320
This is ancient-method paper I made myself.

535
00:24:23,200 --> 00:24:24,080
Ancient-method paper?

536
00:24:24,320 --> 00:24:26,080
Yes, pure ancient-method paper.

537
00:24:26,760 --> 00:24:27,600
You made it?

538
00:24:28,200 --> 00:24:29,240
I made it myself.

539
00:24:29,240 --> 00:24:30,680
All 108 procedures,

540
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:33,320
strictly following the ancient methods,

541
00:24:33,720 --> 00:24:35,080
without a single deviation.

542
00:24:36,280 --> 00:24:37,520
Now this is interesting.

543
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:42,400
Boss Xuan, you may not know this,

544
00:24:42,440 --> 00:24:43,760
but the Forbidden City Museum

545
00:24:43,760 --> 00:24:46,720
is scouring the world for ancient-method paper.

546
00:24:47,040 --> 00:24:48,320
Elder Jiang knows about this.

547
00:24:48,680 --> 00:24:50,560
Director Zeng contacts me daily.

548
00:24:50,560 --> 00:24:52,160
I'm at my wit's end.

549
00:24:52,160 --> 00:24:54,560
Where am I supposed to find this paper?

550
00:24:54,960 --> 00:24:55,400
This...

551
00:24:58,480 --> 00:24:59,200
Elder Jiang,

552
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:01,720
how about you take a look

553
00:25:01,720 --> 00:25:02,280
and examine it?

554
00:25:02,280 --> 00:25:03,080
Master Jiang.

555
00:25:03,760 --> 00:25:04,560
I can't look at it.

556
00:25:04,600 --> 00:25:05,520
You're the expert.

557
00:25:05,520 --> 00:25:06,920
Please just have a look.

558
00:25:06,920 --> 00:25:07,440
You...

559
00:25:08,720 --> 00:25:09,600
I'm not getting involved.

560
00:25:10,880 --> 00:25:11,680
Xuan Yongnian,

561
00:25:13,480 --> 00:25:14,720
you've taken on quite the apprentice.

562
00:25:17,280 --> 00:25:18,440
Sorry you had to see that.

563
00:25:23,360 --> 00:25:24,000
Master Jiang.

564
00:25:28,280 --> 00:25:28,840
Jiang...

565
00:25:33,080 --> 00:25:33,600
Fine.

566
00:25:34,400 --> 00:25:35,160
Alright, alright.

567
00:25:35,160 --> 00:25:36,160
Don't hold out.

568
00:25:36,520 --> 00:25:37,440
I'll take a look for you.

569
00:25:38,320 --> 00:25:39,080
Thank you, Manager Xu.

570
00:25:39,080 --> 00:25:39,880
Let me see.

571
00:25:40,040 --> 00:25:42,920
Biting the hand that feeds you!

572
00:25:49,840 --> 00:25:50,400
Sit down.

573
00:25:51,840 --> 00:25:53,280
Stop adding to the mess.

574
00:25:55,000 --> 00:25:55,760
Thank you.

575
00:26:02,760 --> 00:26:03,480
Elder Jiang.

576
00:26:03,960 --> 00:26:04,760
Elder Jiang.

577
00:26:05,520 --> 00:26:06,760
Come on, take a look.

578
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:08,200
This paper is quite intriguing.

579
00:26:09,240 --> 00:26:10,600
I told you, I'm not getting involved.

580
00:26:14,040 --> 00:26:14,840
Elder Jiang,

581
